To ja ďakujem.

267
00:17:36,639 --> 00:17:39,000
Páni, bohyňa celého vesmíru!

268
00:17:39,008 --> 00:17:41,045
Bohyňa Oh Yun Seo.

269
00:17:41,210 --> 00:17:44,540
