434
00:27:29,097 --> 00:27:31,295
Bože, je taký chladný.

435
00:27:31,933 --> 00:27:34,330
Už by tu mala čoskoro byť.

436
00:27:34,336 --> 00:27:36,235
Správajme sa normálne.

437
00:27:36,905 --> 00:27:38,745
(Oh Yun Seo)

438
00:27:39,808 --> 00:27:42,515
